land Computing Center high memory cluster\nthe name of a DHR B Class steam locomotive\nthe sports teams of Somers High School (New York), a public school\n\n\n== See also ==\nTusk (disambiguation)", "title": "Tusker"}], "error": "max_steps_reached", "wall_time_ms": 1867.7100800000517, "model_target": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct", "model_draft": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct", "seed": 42, "__kind__": "step"}
